                        「持つ」「売る」の判断材料を増やします。
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="forecast-card">
                      <div class="label">愛車の価値予測</div>
                      <div class="price-row">
                        <div class="price" id="forecast-price">183<small>万円</small></div>
                        <div class="delta" id="forecast-tag">半年後 -6万円予測</div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="graph">
                        <svg class="graph-line" viewBox="0 0 300 180" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
                          <defs>
                            <linearGradient id="lineA" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#F84CA2" />
                              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1ddcff" />
                            </linearGradient>
                          </defs>
                          <path d="M10,76 C60,44 88,42 120,62 S190,108 228,120 S270,126 292,138" fill="none" stroke="url(#lineA)" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                          <circle cx="10" cy="76" r="7" fill="#F84CA2"></circle>
                          <circle cx="120" cy="62" r="7" fill="#ff9cc7"></circle>
                          <circle cx="292" cy="138" r="7" fill="#1ddcff"></circle>
